mkdir /usr/share/skipfish
cd /usr/share/skipfish
wget http://skipfish.googlecode.com/files/skipfish-2.10b.tgz
tar -xvzf skipfish-2.10b.tgz
cd skipfish-2.10b
skipfish -m 5 -L -W- -o output_dir -b ie -B <URL>.com http://www.<URL>.com/

Five-connection crawl, but no brute-force; 
pretending to be MSIE and caring less about ambiguous MIME or character set mismatches, 
and trusting <URL>.com links
